    "We devised and then iteratively developed a distinct coding structure for innovation and governance best practices for responsible digital health innovation.",
    "A subsequent analysis and interpretation of this coding structure led to the identification of best practices presented above.",
    "Our research design was focused on making the specific insights of leading digital health practitioners accessible.",
    "As such, the insights presented here are not intended to be fully representative.",
    "However, the study could have further benefited from additional patient and healthcare practitioner perspectives."
